00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:47.440
Exactly.

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:49.840
That Lin Hong'er

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:52.320
brought shame to the entire village.

00:02:52.880 --> 00:02:53.680
That ungrateful girl

00:02:53.880 --> 00:02:56.080
killed her own parents.

00:02:56.160 --> 00:02:57.680
A murderous demon.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:02:58.440
That evil creature.

