00:04:47.200 --> 00:04:48.240
Water...

00:04:50.336 --> 00:04:50.680
My lord.

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:51.440
Bad news.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:52.840
Lady Xu is missing.

00:04:55.640 --> 00:04:57.520
Lin Hong'er wants revenge on Lady Xu.

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.360
If Lady Xu's missing,

00:05:00.200 --> 00:05:01.080
I'm finished.

00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:03.920
Don't just stand there.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:04.600
Go find her.

00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:05.632
Why are you waiting?

00:05:06.176 --> 00:05:07.160
If you fail, we'll die!

00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:08.288
Don't return without her!

00:05:09.728 --> 00:05:10.720
Looks like Lin Hong'er.

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:12.040
She's Lin Hong'er, right?

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:18.280
My dear,

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.080
it's really her.

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:20.000
She's that

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:21.640
Lin Hong'er?

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:23.080
Lin Hong'er?

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.720
- It's truly her.
- That's definitely her!

00:05:26.440 --> 00:05:27.360
Why is she here?

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:28.560
Wasn't she dead?

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:31.400
How dare she return in broad daylight.

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:32.720
She even killed her parents.

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:34.040
She deserves death!

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:38.640
- Murderer!
- Murderer!

00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:46.120
I'm not Lin Hong'er.

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:46.760
Beast!

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:52.440
Your mother...

00:05:52.640 --> 00:05:55.840
I grew up with her since childhood.

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:57.920
I watched her get married.

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:00.960
We gave birth on the same day.

00:06:02.320 --> 00:06:04.160
We nursed our babies together.

00:06:04.560 --> 00:06:07.760
What a kind soul she was!

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:08.840
Monster!

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:11.440
You fiend!

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:12.832
You vile creature!

00:06:12.896 --> 00:06:13.800
Worse than an animal!

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:15.080
I'm not Lin Hong'er!

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.200
You are Lin Hong'er!

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:18.200
You beast!

00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:19.680
Brute!

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:22.280
You vile creature!

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:28.400
Everyone, stop!

00:06:28.400 --> 00:06:28.960
Stop!

00:06:29.480 --> 00:06:30.360
- Stop!
- Move aside!

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:31.760
Make way!

00:06:31.880 --> 00:06:32.880
What are you doing?

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:34.680
Save me.

00:06:35.480 --> 00:06:36.680
Kill them all.

00:06:36.880 --> 00:06:38.360
Kill them all!

00:06:39.400 --> 00:06:41.600
You're such a heartless villain.

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:45.160
Who are you?

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:46.080
Guards!

00:06:46.280 --> 00:06:46.800
Yes, my lord.

00:06:47.520 --> 00:06:49.000
Imprison Lin Hong'er.

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:49.880
Understood.

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:51.480
- Wonderful!
- Lock her up!

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:52.680
I'm not Lin Hong'er.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:53.440
Move!

00:06:53.880 --> 00:06:54.560
Let go of me!

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:56.280
It's over.

00:06:57.160 --> 00:06:58.080
It's over.

00:06:58.080 --> 00:06:59.240
It's over.

00:07:00.920 --> 00:07:02.560
It's all over.

00:07:03.960 --> 00:07:07.080
Lin Hong'er must have captured Lady Xu.

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:09.120
It's over!

00:07:09.160 --> 00:07:09.720
My lord.

00:07:09.760 --> 00:07:10.280
My lord.

00:07:10.280 --> 00:07:10.800
My lord,

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:11.840
great news!

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:13.040
What great news?

00:07:13.040 --> 00:07:14.080
Are you mocking me?

00:07:14.520 --> 00:07:14.920
No!

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:15.320
My lord,

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:17.280
Lin Hong'er has been captured.

00:07:17.640 --> 00:07:18.200
Really?

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:19.640
Without doubt.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:21.560
Someone just reported

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:22.920
that he's seen Lin Hong'er.

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.560
The Registrar personally led the team.

00:07:25.520 --> 00:07:26.840
Lin Hong'er

00:07:26.840 --> 00:07:27.800
is utterly wicked

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:28.960
and infamous.

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:31.600
This time, the Registrar
caught her red-handed.

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.640
The people are cheering in approval.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:35.400
They're even hailing you as wise.

00:07:36.760 --> 00:07:37.680
Of course!

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:40.800
Though the Registrar made the arrest,

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:44.720
it was my planning that enabled it.

00:07:44.720 --> 00:07:45.440
Absolutely.

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:46.440
Let's go.

00:07:46.440 --> 00:07:47.160
Lead the way.

00:07:47.440 --> 00:07:48.120
My lord, please.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.120
Han,

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:50.320
you arrested Lin Hong'er...

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:51.720
My lord.

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:55.160
Why are you here?

00:07:56.360 --> 00:07:58.800
I heard Lin Hong'er was captured,

00:07:59.240 --> 00:08:00.240
so I came specifically

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.320
to testify against her crimes.

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:09.200
Good.

00:08:09.480 --> 00:08:11.800
A wise person knows when to yield.

00:08:12.000 --> 00:08:13.560
Your decision to turn over a new leaf

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:15.560
brings me great relief.

00:08:15.720 --> 00:08:16.240
My lord,

00:08:16.600 --> 00:08:18.320
she claims to be close with Lin Hong'er.

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:19.080
Are her words

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:20.080
credible?

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:21.120
Of course.

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:24.200
I oversaw this case.

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:26.200
As the presiding official,

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:27.920
how could I not know?

00:08:29.040 --> 00:08:30.160
Come with me.

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:42.640
I've finally caught you.

00:08:57.920 --> 00:08:58.800
You...

00:08:59.480 --> 00:09:01.840
You've colluded together.

00:09:10.880 --> 00:09:14.160
Are you Lin Hong'er or Lady Xu?

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:14.800
Ugh!

00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:17.240
He Laijin,

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:19.160
you traitorous creature.

00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:21.400
Yes!

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:22.800
It's just this glare.

00:09:23.560 --> 00:09:25.160
Y-You're Lady Xu?

00:09:26.640 --> 00:09:28.800
H-How did this happen?

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:31.120
Wrong arrest!

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:32.320
My lord, you're mistaken.

00:09:32.760 --> 00:09:33.280
She...

00:09:33.440 --> 00:09:36.240
She was denounced
by all the Lin family's neighbors

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:39.320
and testified against by me,
her former accomplice.

00:09:39.600 --> 00:09:40.040
She...

00:09:40.560 --> 00:09:42.040
She's unquestionably

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:43.120
the heinous criminal

00:09:43.520 --> 00:09:45.080
who killed her own parents.

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:46.720
She's not!

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:47.320
My lord.

00:09:47.560 --> 00:09:48.320
Everyone, out!

00:09:48.520 --> 00:09:49.800
I'll interrogate her myself.

00:09:50.120 --> 00:09:50.880
Leave!

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:51.480
My lord.

00:09:53.640 --> 00:09:54.480
What now?

00:09:55.040 --> 00:09:55.480
My lord,

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:56.640
someone is beating the drum.

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.040
Han,

00:09:58.040 --> 00:09:58.920
handle this.

00:09:59.400 --> 00:10:00.040
- Understood.
- My lord,

00:10:00.240 --> 00:10:01.920
they are victims of the Lin family case.

00:10:02.040 --> 00:10:04.160
They said there was a grave injustice.

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:10.040
Make way!

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:11.936
The Perfect's here.

00:10:14.920 --> 00:10:16.440
Bring the petitioners to the hall.

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:16.880
Understood.

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:22.720
My lord.

00:10:23.560 --> 00:10:23.920
My lord,

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:24.760
I'm innocent!

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.040
- My lord.
- My lord,

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:27.360
Lin Hong'er is innocent.

00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:29.800
She didn't kill her parents!

00:10:36.600 --> 00:10:37.920
The money is for you both.

00:10:38.440 --> 00:10:39.600
Can I give her some water?

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:53.040
The mansion's wedding procession
is already on route.

00:10:53.520 --> 00:10:55.160
It'll arrive tomorrow.

00:10:55.320 --> 00:10:57.600
Should I inform Xiao Xian

00:10:57.800 --> 00:10:59.320
to take a different route

00:11:00.040 --> 00:11:01.800
and pick you up from prison?

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:02.360
You...

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:11.440
Aren't you trying to steal her life?

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:17.520
This is the reality

00:11:18.000 --> 00:11:19.440
she actually endured.

00:11:29.800 --> 00:11:31.080
(The trial is ongoing.)

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:32.720
(Why did Master Xu send someone here?)

00:11:37.320 --> 00:11:40.360
You serve Master Xu's?

00:11:43.320 --> 00:11:44.080
That's great!

00:11:51.720 --> 00:11:54.640
What should I do
about Lady Xu's situation?

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:57.200
Didn't I already fetch someone

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:58.480
to resolve this?

00:12:01.600 --> 00:12:02.200
Someone?

00:12:05.240 --> 00:12:06.600
Those two from the Luo family?

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:09.760
The Luos were bribed by Master Xu.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.320
You know this well.

00:12:11.920 --> 00:12:13.000
Exactly.

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:15.040
But their theatrics today

00:12:15.320 --> 00:12:17.000
makes it more confusing to me.

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:18.440
I suspended the trial

00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:19.560
and came over right away.

00:12:23.240 --> 00:12:25.920
Are you saying these were arranged
by Master Xu?

00:12:26.400 --> 00:12:28.680
Now the whole city knows
Lin Hong'er is alive.

00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:31.320
And Lady Xu was taken away

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:32.160
in broad daylight.

00:12:32.680 --> 00:12:33.680
Do you intend to

00:12:34.040 --> 00:12:35.320
publicly reveal the secret

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:38.320
that Lady Xu and Lin Hong'er
look identical?

00:12:39.920 --> 00:12:40.880
To put it bluntly,

00:12:41.280 --> 00:12:42.880
do you want to thoroughly investigate

00:12:42.880 --> 00:12:44.040
every single matter?

00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:45.280
Of course not.

00:12:46.640 --> 00:12:48.080
Absolutely not.

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:49.000
So

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:51.840
only Lin Hong'er
can be the one arrested.

00:12:53.120 --> 00:12:53.760
There's

00:12:53.760 --> 00:12:54.960
only one way to save her.

00:12:58.360 --> 00:12:59.320
Reopen the case.

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:06.080
But to reopen the case,

00:13:06.400 --> 00:13:07.920
we need a culprit.

00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:09.880
I've already prepared
the culprit for you.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:11.400
The Luo family's testimony

00:13:11.400 --> 00:13:13.040
will explain everything clearly.

00:13:17.600 --> 00:13:18.480
Very well.

00:13:19.040 --> 00:13:19.720
I see.

00:13:20.680 --> 00:13:22.600
I'll overturn Lin Hong'er's verdict now.

00:13:25.920 --> 00:13:27.320
A toast with tea instead of wine.

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:30.200
Thank you for granting me
this brilliant strategy.

00:13:34.040 --> 00:13:35.280
I'll overturn it immediately.

00:13:42.278 --> 00:13:48.614
♪Fate begins and ends, I sip the past♪

00:13:48.614 --> 00:13:54.275
♪Love and hatred flow endlessly♪

00:13:55.206 --> 00:14:02.822
♪When spring comes, I see the truth♪

00:14:02.822 --> 00:14:08.921
♪We've changed through the years♪

00:14:08.921 --> 00:14:15.590
♪Cold lamps reflect pear blossom dew♪

00:14:15.590 --> 00:14:23.270
♪Worlds change as streams run west♪

00:14:23.270 --> 00:14:30.296
♪Rains veil hills, gathering sorrows♪

00:14:30.296 --> 00:14:36.454
♪In deep courtyards, hands drift apart♪